@startuml
[*] --> Anonymous
Anonymous --> Authenticating : submit credentials
Authenticating --> Rejected : user missing/password invalid
Authenticating --> Rejected : account inactive
Authenticating --> Authenticated : password valid
Authenticated --> TokenIssued : sign JWT
TokenIssued --> ProfileLoaded : GET /me with bearer token
ProfileLoaded --> ProfileUpdated : PATCH /me
ProfileUpdated --> ProfileLoaded : reload profile
Rejected --> Anonymous : retry
TokenIssued --> [*]
@enduml
